   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Turn the drain valve counter clockwise to open the drain valve
on the bottom of the fuel prefilter.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Drain some fuel (and any water) until clean fuel flows from the
pre-filter.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
